  "text": "It is reasonable for the feature function u m (x) to be independent of another individual's feature func- tion u m (x), but we would like for each of the components within a particular function u m (x) to have a structured prior. Rather than use independent Gaussian processes for each of the K scalar component functions in u m (x), we use a multi-task GP as in [CITATION_1] and Bonilla et al. (2008) . We perform a pointwise linear transformation of K independent latent functions using a matrix L Σ U that is the Cholesky decomposition of an inter-task covariance matrix Σ U , i.e.,",
